The exercise files for this tutorial are arranged in the following folders:

basicExample/
-----------------------
This folder contains a basic example with the AIR installer badge.  

expressInstallExample/
-----------------------
This folder contains the full AIR Badge Installer example with Express Installation.

sample/
-----------------------
This folder contains the sample AIR application that you can use to test the install badge.

src/
-----------------------
This folder contains the InstallBadge.js in an uncompressed format.  You can customize this file to suit your needs.  This directory also includes the files needed with the InstallBadge.js file (the Express Installation SWF File, the Installer Badge, and the AC_RunActiveContent.js file).

Questions and comments can be directed to my blog, http://www.davidtucker.net/.